      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> and cook, covered, for 4-5 min or until tender</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
